  %h2 AgreeList's mission: increase the quality of decision making
  %p
    AgreeList wants to improve decision making by developing a tool which:
    %ul
      %li Gathers and organizes trackable opinions by storing them in a unique database, promoting constructive debates
      %li Favors plurality of opinions fighting the polarization of opinions, including those little supported by traditional medias
      %li Shows in real time what people think and why, on both sides of controversial topics
